      "remarks": [
        "Annual onset hazard from age 12 to 55. Female 0.0022/yr (~9% lifetime), male 0.0011/yr ",
        "(~4.6% lifetime); a history of depression ('depression' attribute from the depression ",
        "module or 'mdd' from veteran_mdd) raises the hazard ~2.5x."
